Author: cartoonz0mbie
Text: I don't think I've ever had a shred of confidence lol. There are a few times where I'll walk past a reflective surface and in that brief moment I don't think I look fat. So I go to investigate further and then the body dysmorphia kicks in again lol. The crash is so much worse than the high
